    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior is pristine and shows no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, reflecting its history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage.",
